messageBody:
Please note that I am referring to the unification of vowels at this
point. I will concede that striking #20 from the alphabet is perhaps
a bit much, but I can still see no reason to keep all three of
the "ah"'s.

point.  I will concede that striking #20 from the alphabet is perhaps 
a bit much, but I can still see no reason to keep all three of 
the "ah"'s.
